title: 2018–19 Midland Football League
text:
The 2018–19 Midland Football League season was the 5th in the history of the <a href="Midland%20Football%20League%20%282014%29">Midland Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in England. The provisional club allocations for steps 5 and 6 were announced by the FA on 25 May.
